data.description: New paint, carpet & more! Idyllic setting meets sunrise lit panoramic Mt. Rainier & Puget Sound views. Perched high on 100' of high bank waterfront & quietly at the end of a horse dotted lane, this NW Contemporary home with its circular flow is flanked by living spaces. Tongue & groove wood showcases the vaulted ceilings in the open living/dining area & primary ensuite where forest & Puget Sound views fill the rooms. A cozy glow from the brick fireplace adds warmth to the wood ceilings & the dramatic wall of view windows that reach to the ceiling. You'll enjoy the  backyard and the expansive deck. Upstairs two bedrooms, full bath & the primary view ensuite w/balcony & office. King Co. Parks is a neighbor to the north w/nearby beach access.
